videos.headline: Ohio WR and QB connect on reverse pass
videos.description: Ohio's Nathan Rourke and Andrew Meyer switch roles as Meyer gets the ball in the backfield and completes the pass to Rourke down the sideline.

videos.headline: Rourke finds Knock for Ohio's opening-drive TD
videos.description: Ohio's Nathan Rourke shows patience after the play-fake to find DL Knock who finds space in the end zone.

videos.headline: White explodes for 56-yard Ohio TD
videos.description: Ohio's Papi White leaves his defender in the dust and catches a beautiful ball from Nathan Rourke and runs into the end zone to go up 13-0.

videos.headline: Ohio keeps UAB scoreless with blocked FG
videos.description: UAB attempts a field goal but Ohio generates pressure up the middle and Cleon Aloese blocks the kick.

videos.headline: UAB defenders collide on explosive Ohio run
videos.description: Ohio's Dorian Brown flashes the speed after two UAB defenders collide on his way to an electric 74-yard touchdown as Ohio leads 20-0.

videos.headline: Brown drags UAB defenders across goal line for Ohio TD
videos.description: Dorian Brown takes the carry and rumbles  through UAB defenders for the 9-yard score to go up 27-3.

videos.headline: Brown runs untouched for Ohio TD
videos.description: Ohio's Dorian Brown follows his blockers down the middle for a 35-yard touchdown run to go up 34-6.

videos.headline: Ohio up to more trickery with reverse flea-flicker
videos.description: Ohio QB Nathan Rourke hands the ball off to start the reverse but gets it back before completing a pass to Troy Mangen for 24 yards.

videos.headline: Brown unstoppable with 4th TD
videos.description: Dorian Brown continues his monster day against UAB with a 14-yard touchdown run to give him 120 yards and 4 touchdowns on only 8 carries.

videos.headline: Brown, Bobcats blow out UAB in Bahamas Bowl
videos.description: Ohio's Dorian Brown rushes for 152 yards and four touchdowns in the dominating 41-6 win over UAB.
